HEADWORD: Whiplash injury
<hw>Whip"lash` in"ju*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>an injury
to the neck caused by the sudden motion of the head backward and
forward, as occurs to the occupants of a vehicle hit from behind by
another vehicle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

